TY  - JOUR
T1  - When Do Spinouts Enhance Parent Firm Performance? Evidence from the U.S. Automobile Industry, 1890–1986
AU  - Ioannou, Ioannis
Y1  - 2013/08/22
PY  - 2013
DA  - 2014/04/01
